你休息完再一齊同大家出黎<br />\n唔需要自責今次出唔到嚟會點<br />\n因為你都曾經為香港出一分力<br />\n多謝你 老套個講 休息是為了走更長的路<br />\n加油 共勉之"},{"pid":"82d53d56f91203052063e5b51f7cc2c91d87f33a","tid":1336892,"uid":110039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T08:50:29.000Z","msg":"反而我因為重有抗爭既機會而興奮，唔識攰。最重要重未輸"},{"pid":"dd39dc9a858b042db7b2024da84baadea9f67c66","tid":1336892,"uid":279357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:00:40.000Z","msg":"加油丫<br />\n等你"},{"pid":"3363e196d0cac1624c5b8030dca8cac4074c4882","tid":1336892,"uid":146883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:02:55.000Z","msg":"去！個個都好攰！為香港，你還在猶豫甚麼？"},{"pid":"15499861d77cbcd993dee8d523a08cb0e93e7f95","tid":1336892,"uid":224408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:06:00.000Z","msg":"大家加油 已出 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xr3rQ4D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXr3rQ4D.png&h=abfc1fdb&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}